title: Ep 36: Find Yourself Then Get Over Yourself
description: Who the hell are you? What is this thing we call the self? Philosophy has some answers, but so does Sam Harris. Also, in all the books on self improvement I've read, they say you must get over yourself to be successful and happy. So which is it? Do I find myself or get over it to be happy?
author: nadav@ymhstudios.com (Christina Pazsitzky)
